\n就隻隻都短炒變長揸，成手蟹貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"感謝大大，牛熊都得，星期一開始每次寫低，入咗貨即set出價，當考自己眼光，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問點可以改心態，睇住隻股放咗就係咁上，個心好撚嬲嗰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12106205dd9bfa886f3d6b23d3f8d07285fb7d1","tid":766190,"uid":34286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"夠膽輸<br />\n唔夠膽贏"},{"pid":"8347ac0adfebcc571f23c3209b6a04528147d7c5","tid":766190,"uid":21913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12106205dd9bfa886f3d6b23d3f8d07285fb7d1","tid":766190,"uid":34286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"夠膽輸<br />\n唔夠膽贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"正確，心態倒轉就掂，但實際操作好難"},{"pid":"18ee0900041f0570c6a21d50ca90b7f8b9747f03","tid":766190,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:20:10.000Z","msg":"唔止蝕<br />\n跌到仆街"},{"pid":"b6a956086a6e2523e43c4e70946eb24620b19adf","tid":766190,"uid":67635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:24:28.000Z","msg":"升既股票會照顧自己<br />\n輸既股票你要照顧佢，唔對路就要止蝕<br />\n<br />\n但散戶心態相反<br />\n輸緊個d覺得有一日會反彈扑暈自己唔理<br />\n反而升緊個d就時時刻刻望住<br />\n驚利潤會消失，甚至提早止盈<br />\n<br />\n同埋散戶好鍾意買入賣出一野咁去<br />\n買應該要先小注，形態大好就加碼<br />\n當上升動力減弱就開始減持<br />\n<br />\n咁先可以減低風險，又可以保住最大利潤<br />\n因為只有神先知道最底點，最高點"},{"pid":"a93bf38423dca74ff7febdbfa299813fbb622b14","tid":766190,"uid":24824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:26:12.000Z","msg":"因為升少少既時候就急急腳走<br />\n而跌多多既時候就坐死唔止蝕"},{"pid":"776fe6d90b319e85727c53d2b2e6095496a9b774","tid":766190,"uid":49648,"like":0,"disl